## Source: ossf-package-analysis (cb6c7e45daf2eb5fe472bf38bfa221edfd5d7dd0e5fe9f62638f799e7fe78fe8)
The OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'rosetta-elements' @ 3.0.0 (npm) as malicious.

It is considered malicious because:

- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.
